Close an 'undo' stack (See tv_UndoOpenStack)

// [PARAMETERS]
iText    string    The text of the closed undo stack

// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

tv_redo [iText]

Do a redo

// [PARAMETERS]
iText    string    The text of the previous undo stack (beause this command close it before making the redo)

// [RETURN]
0|1    bool    A redo was done or not

